comments: Conley (UTA) establishes a legal screening position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Temple (BKN).
Irving (BKN) moves legally alongside of Mitchell's (UTA) path during his driving shot attempt and cleanly dislodges the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal arm to arm contact allowing Irving (BKN) to play through the contact and continue his drive.
Mitchell (UTA) directs the ball after the made basket and Utah is correctly assessed a Delay of Game Violation.
Jordan (UTA) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and disengage in the post.
Ingles (UTA) cleanly dislodges the ball during Jordan's (BKN) shot at the rim.
As Ingles (UTA) gathers the ball, Jordan (BKN) gets his hand on the ball, cleanly dislodging the ball from Ingles. Ingles then legally re-gathers the ball.
Prince (BKN) legally contests Gobert's (UTA) shot at the rim as he does not make contact with Gobert's head.
Harris (BKN) jumps legally up and down attempting to retrieve the rebound as he does not deliver contact to Ingles (UTA).
Gobert's (UTA) collapses his left forearm against his body while maintaining a vertical arm during Irving's (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Conley (UTA) is in a legal picking position as he is firmed up and does not deliver contact to Temple (BKN).
As Mitchell's (UTA) momentum is already taking him in that direction, Irving's (BKN) rested hand makes marginal contact with Mitchell during the driving shot attempt.
Jordan (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Gobert (UTA).
Irving (BKN) briefly places his hand to Ingles' (UTA) leg, but immediately disengages sliding his hand off.
Ingles (UTA) moves legally alongside of Irving (BKN) and makes marginal contact with Irving's arm while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Irving (BKN) makes marginal contact with Conley (UTA) on the perimeter.

Shooting foul was initially called on Temple (BKN) for illegal contact to Conley (UTA). Replay review pursuant to a coachs challenge was deemed successful as Temple legally gets to the ball on the jump shot attempt by Conley.
As the ball is being tipped to Harris (BKN) after the jump ball, Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal contact to Harris allowing Harris to retrieve the ball.
Jordan (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position as he firms up and does not extend his leg into Ingles' (UTA) path.
Ingles (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Irving (BKN).
Irving (BKN) makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) arm causing Gobert to lose control of the ball.
Irving (BKN) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Bogdanovic (UTA) jumps legally up and down and does not apply force with his forearm to Prince's (BKN) back legally tipping the ball out during the rebound.
Mitchell (UTA) legally retrieves the ball in the back court as Bogdanovic (UTA) never gained full possession of the ball in the front court.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
